comments.body:
@timstclair unless you have evidence otherwise, i'd expect this is just _adding_ GoogleHadoopFileSystem, not making GHFS the only option

fyi, @wattsteve maintains https://wiki.apache.org/hadoop/HCFS, which suggests that are ~12 such filesystem implementations.

@zmerlynn imho,the question is if we should include hcfs plugins in the image or not. since realistically there are maybe 3 or 4 that are relevant and available (some are prioprietary and not distributable), i'm for including them in the image instead of providing separate images for each or making the image pluggable.
